inda tired to hear that they are the same.. soooo..<br>
<br>
kick raises by 4 points per level<br>
bash/slam raise by 5 points per level<br>
<br>
so for most of the life of a warrior slam or bash will be better, especially with the stun<br>
<br>
on the other hand, bash caps at 240, kick at 210 and slam at 200<br>
<br>
what does it mean ? well simply that bash is by far the best of the 3, but it forces you to wield only one weapon, or to use a hotkey combo, and it's not always to do when you have to run around to taunt everything...<br>
<br>
kick caps higher than slam, however kick raises slower and only stuns after 55<br>
<br>
so to make it short slam is better than kick from level 1 to 58, and kick is then better because for the first time your kick skill is higher and you have the stun component in the skill<br>
<br>
slam also doesnt work while in wolf form while kick and bash do<br>
<br>
to make it short, use bash if you can, otherwise slam til 58 and kick at 59-60 and while in wolf form<br>
